Package cisc275.group3.model.scene

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Scene
    Simplest base class of a scene supporting methods shared by all subclasses.
    SceneBay
    Bay scene/model.
    SceneBeach
    Beach scene/model.
    SceneBeachMini
    Bonus Beach mini-game to be unlocked after completing a beach mission.
    SceneHQ
    HQ scene/model.
    SceneInventory
    Inventory scene/model.
    SceneTitle
    SceneTitle extends scene and is used to represent the title screen
    SceneTutorial
    SceneTutorial.java is a special instance of Scene.java
    SceneWetland
    Wetland scene/model.
